{
  "stem": "1680.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he came down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He didn't have his shoes on, because he was napping.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they put him also like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Whoever was in this building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What happened was in the back of this building was a church.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And somebody shoot from the church to the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they came, ran all around to see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in the meantime, when-- the people that went to the other side, in the church, found some Polish people there, what they were shooting to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they took them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And at that time, they let us go, but it didn't-- it wasn't too much of a-- think that we would be shot, all three of us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was one time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next time was when they start grabbing people on the street to clean up the war-- the messes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, they came into the park.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they parked their trucks in the park, and they start washing themselves and eating and threw away can with the things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they kept Jewish people on the street to clean up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was between them, because I didn't have-- I didn't have any patience to sit in the house, because I was single and young.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was always on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's why I was always in danger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they took me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at that time, it was not so bad, because they grabbed you for a few hours, then they let you go.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then started, again, with trucks that they took people away from town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it took a week or 10 days until you found out where they-- from the relatives, where they have.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was a camp not too far from town, which was called Pskov.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
